Class RateLimitedDispatcher

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class RateLimitedDispatcher
extends Object

    Rate-limiting support. Some message fabrics simply should not be used to send a lot of messages.

    Donal Fellows

      • setCooldownSeconds

        public void setCooldownSeconds(int cooldownSeconds)
        Set how long must elapse between updates to the status of any particular user. Calls before that time are just silently dropped.
        Parameters:
        cooldownSeconds - Time to elapse, in seconds.
